          definition "A unit of pressure equal to 1,000 bars (Symbol: kb)"
      partOfSpeech noun
    entry
      definitions
        entry
          definition "A length of double-stranded DNA containing two thousand nucleotides, one thousand on each strand"
        entry
          definition "A length of single-stranded RNA containing one thousand nucleotides"
